## 1.8 ARB AUDIT P0 BLOCKERS (docs/ENGINEERING_AUDIT_ARB_2026-07-22.md) — 2026-07-22
> Full evidence + 18 reports in the audit file. These are production blockers.
- [x] **C1 — RLS not enforced → FIXED + APPLIED + PROVEN LIVE (2026-07-22).** Migrations 010+011
      applied to live Supabase via MCP; 28/28 tables FORCE RLS; hostyllo_app proven fail-closed
      (no/wrong ctx → 0 rows, correct → own only). Role has LOGIN (pw set, rotate advised),
      bypassrls=false. ⚠️ App-side activation pending: set DATABASE_URL_APP in Railway (Hobby plan
      pending). Also applied live: 008 (rent idx) + adapted-009 (auth columns — fixed a live login
      crash). Migration 010:
      FORCE ROW LEVEL SECURITY on all 28 tables + every policy rewritten to
      `hostel_id = current_setting('app.hostel_id') OR current_setting('app.system_context')='on'`;
      hostels service_role policy → tenant scoping on id; least-privilege `hostyllo_app` role
      (system_context='off', RLS-bound) vs privileged `postgres` (system_context='on', auth+workers).
      lib/db.ts: withTenant now uses `tenantPool` (DATABASE_URL_APP → hostyllo_app); forgotten filter
      = 0 rows. SAFE FALLBACK: inert until DATABASE_URL_APP set → no lockout risk. scripts/verify-rls.sql
      = gate. ⚠️ FOUNDER: apply mig 010, create hostyllo_app LOGIN+password, set DATABASE_URL_APP,
      run verify-rls.sql (0 rows), prove raw SELECT w/o app.hostel_id returns 0 rows.
- [x] **C2 — weak ENCRYPTION_KEY → FIXED.** lib/env.ts `assertEncryptionKey()` rejects unset /
      wrong-length / low-entropy (<16 distinct bytes) keys at boot; auth.ts uses it. Local .env key
      rotated to a real `randomBytes(32)`. ⚠️ any TOTP secret enrolled under the OLD key must be
      re-enrolled (pre-launch → likely none).
- [x] **C3 — secrets hygiene → FIXED (repo side).** `apps/api/.env.example` template added (incl.
      DATABASE_URL_APP, SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN, empty secrets) + rotate-first runbook. .env already
      gitignored. ⚠️ FOUNDER: rotate ALL live creds (they lived in a working-tree .env) + move to
      Railway/Vercel secret store.
- [x] **C4 — verify-pitr.sh → FIXED.** Now requires `SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN` (PAT) for the Management
      API instead of the service_role JWT (which always 401'd). Gate can pass once a PAT is provided.
- [x] **M1 — FIXED.** Canonical connection layer (buildSsl + privileged pool + tenantPool +
      withTenant + dbHealthCheck) consolidated into `packages/db/src/withTenant.ts`; apps/api/lib/db.ts
      is now a thin re-export. One pool, TLS verified, no insecure duplicate instantiated on import.
- [x] **M2 — FIXED.** Root CLAUDE.md `docs/docs/`→`docs/` (5 refs); GROUND TRUTH rewritten to reality
      (10 migrations, 16 routes, all defects+C1-C4 fixed); git-discipline branch note corrected to Develop.
- [x] **M3 — FIXED.** `packages/db/migrate.mjs` runner + `schema_migrations` ledger, tx-per-file,
      checksum drift warnings, `baseline` mode for the hand-migrated DB. Scripts + migrations/README.md.
- [x] **M4 — FIXED.** `lib/env.ts validateEnv()` — required secrets throw in prod / warn in dev;
      rejects public cookie placeholder; server.ts calls it at boot; cookie/CORS fail-open defaults
      now dev-only.
- [x] **M5 — DONE + CI GREEN (run 29920423462).** Created `buildApp()` factory (app.ts) + slim
